reviewText: I am so excited to finally be able to get the full video of this show, which I wish I could have attended. Of course I saw the Habibi clip on Baalbek's site, one of the most exciting live moments on video I have ever seen, and of course I wanted the rest of the show, had to have it, in fact. I am so glad it is finally available on DVD and will post a review as soon as it arrives. I have high expectations.
